<TEXT>
<P>
 E. John Lewis, 78, a founder of the Pacifica radio network.With his friend 
Lewis Hill, Lewis started the Pacifica Foundation in 1949 with station KPFA in 
Berkeley. The station became known for its liberal posture and by the 1960s was 
one of the leading voices in the country against the Vietnam War. Lewis, a 
