REGIONAL ROUNDUP: PETOSEED CO. ACQUIRES DUTCH SEED MARKETER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Petoseed Co. Inc., a Saticoy-based vegetable seed producer, said it has 
acquired Royal Sluis, a Dutch seed marketer. 
</P>
<P>
 Petoseed, which is a privately held company, did not disclose the value of the 
deal. 
</P>
<P>
 The company said it plans to combine its research and seed production 
organizations with Royal Sluis', and streamline them. Royal Sluis will operate 
as a separate business unit within Petoseed and retain its brand name. 
</P>
<P>
 Petoseed said it is one of the top five producers of hybrid seeds worldwide. 
It sells seed chiefly to commercial growers. 
