 Attendance is free. The Costa Mesa Republican Assembly is sponsoring the 
forum. 
</P>
<P>
 A total of 12 candidates are running for two open seats on the council. Peter 
F. Buffa, an incumbent, is seeking a third term, and Jay Humphrey is stepping 
down after four years of service. 
</P>
