<TEXT>
<P>
 Prop. 187 -- A headline in Saturday editions of The Times incorrectly 
described the margin by which Proposition 187 leads in the latest Times poll. 
Among likely voters, the measure is favored by 59% and opposed by 33% -- less 
than a 2-1 margin. 
</P>
